			&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Barometer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;A&amp;nbsp;barometer&amp;nbsp;is an instrument&amp;nbsp;used to measure air pressure&amp;nbsp;as it varies with distance either above or below sea level.&lt;br /&gt;
